01:52:12,625 --> 01:52:14,166
<font color="#ffff00">Kurasa begitu.</font>

433
01:52:28,625 --> 01:52:30,457
<font color="#ffff00">Mari kita cari tahu sekarang.</font>

434
01:52:31,625 --> 01:52:33,041
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

