01:52:44,500 --> 01:52:46,499
<font color="#ffff00">Berdiri di situ.</font>

436
01:52:48,333 --> 01:52:49,332
<font color="#ffff00">Apa?</font>

437
01:52:56,542 --> 01:52:57,624
<font color="#ffff00">Apa yang kau lihat?</font>

438
01:53:01,625 --> 01:53:03,291
<font color="#ffff00">Terlihat sama saja.</font>

439
01:53:03,708 --> 01:53:05,374
<font color="#ffff00">Apa tidak lebih gelap?</font>

440
01:53:06,583 --> 01:53:08,166
<font color="#ffff00">Mungkin tidak.</font>

441
01:53:10,458 --> 01:53:12,374
<font color="#ffff00">Itu kelihatan lebih gelap bagiku.</font>

442
01:53:14,708 --> 01:53:16,707
<font color="#ffff00">Aku tak melihat bedanya.</font>

443
01:53:18,417 --> 01:53:20,916
<font color="#ffff00">Ini, lihat!</font>

444
01:53:21,542 --> 01:53:23,874
<font color="#ffff00">Bayangannya harus lebih gelap
